sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant MM as ModelMesh<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Runtime Container<br/>(Triton/MLServer/OVMS)
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Puller as Puller Sidecar<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as External Storage<br/>S3/GCS/Azure 443/TCP

    Note over Client,MM: Flow 1: gRPC Inference Request
    Client->>MM: gRPC inference request<br/>8033/TCP, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MM->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>gRPC (localhost/UDS)
    Runtime-->>MM: Inference result
    MM->>etcd: Update model state<br/>2379/TCP, Optional TLS/mTLS
    MM-->>Client: gRPC response

    Note over Client,RESTProxy: Flow 2: REST Inference Request (via OAuth)
    Client->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS POST /v2/models/:predict<br/>8443/TCP TLS, OAuth token
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthProxy: Validate OAuth token<br/>SAR: get services
    OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: Forward (pre-authenticated)<br/>8008/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    RESTProxy->>MM: Translate REST→gRPC<br/>8033/TCP, Optional TLS
    MM->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>gRPC (localhost/UDS)
    Runtime-->>MM: Inference result
    MM-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
    RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP response
    OAuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Controller,Storage: Flow 3: Model Loading
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch Predictor CR changes<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Controller->>MM: registerModel / setVModel<br/>8033/TCP gRPC, Optional TLS
    MM->>etcd: Store model metadata<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    MM->>Puller: Trigger model download<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    Puller->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, Storage creds
    Storage-->>Puller: Model artifacts
    Puller->>Runtime: Load model via adapter<br/>8085/TCP or UDS
    Runtime-->>MM: Model loaded confirmation

    Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Controller Reconciliation
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch CRDs (ServingRuntime, Predictor)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Deployment<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Manage HPA, ConfigMaps, Secrets<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA token

    Note over etcd,Controller: Flow 5: Event-Driven Reconciliation
    etcd-->>Controller: Model/VModel state change event<br/>(ModelMesh Event Stream watcher)
    Controller->>Controller: Convert to GenericEvent<br/>Trigger Predictor reconcile
